Paper: hep-th/0202164

Date: 2002-02-24

Title: Spacetime structure of massive gravitino

Authors: M. Kirchbach, D. V. Ahluwalia

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B529 (2002) 124-131

We present reasons as to why an ab initio analysis of the spacetime structureof massive gravitino is necessary. Afterwards, we construct the relevantrepresentation space, and finally, give a new physical interpretation ofmassive gravitino.